      "tree": {
        "sha": "8f03c39864a34d59068d3b02c6259ce680b1623c",
        "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/git/trees/8f03c39864a34d59068d3b02c6259ce680b1623c"
      },
      "verification": {
        "verified": true,
        "reason": "valid",
        "payload": "tree 8f03c39864a34d59068d3b02c6259ce680b1623c\nparent 88e071667bf27cd811ef4e3fdcdcd85ac91b717a\nauthor MarcoFalke <*~=`'#}+{/-|&$^_@721217.xyz> 1765716623 +0100\ncommitter fanquake <fanquake@gmail.com> 1772193667 +0000\n\nnetif: fix compilation warning in QueryDefaultGatewayImpl()\n\n```\nsrc/common/netif.cpp:137:51: error: comparison of integers of different signs: 'int64_t' (aka 'long') and 'unsigned long' [-Werror,-Wsign-compare]\n  137 |         for (nlmsghdr* hdr = (nlmsghdr*)response; NLMSG_OK(hdr, recv_result); hdr = NLMSG_NEXT(hdr, recv_result)) {\n      |                                                   ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\n/usr/include/netlink/netlink.h:220:31: note: expanded from macro 'NLMSG_OK'\n  220 | #define NLMSG_OK(_hdr, _len)            NL_ITEM_OK(_hdr, _len, NLMSG_HDRLEN, _NLMSG_LEN)\n      |                                         ^                ~~~~  ~~~~~~~~~~~~\n/usr/include/netlink/netlink.h:203:10: note: expanded from macro 'NL_ITEM_OK'\n  203 |         ((_len) >= _hlen && _LEN_M(_ptr) >= _hlen && _LEN_M(_ptr) <= (_len))\n      |           ~~~~  ^  ~~~~~\n1 error generated.\n```\n\nHappens on FreeBSD 15.0, with the default compiler (Clang 19).\n\nOn FreeBSD 14, `/usr/include/netlink/netlink.h` contains:\n```\n #define NLMSG_HDRLEN                    ((int)sizeof(struct nlmsghdr))\n```\n\nOn FreeBSD 15, `/usr/include/netlink/netlink.h` contains:\n```\n #define NLMSG_HDRLEN                    (sizeof(struct nlmsghdr))\n```\n\nCo-authored-by: Hennadii Stepanov <32963518+hebasto@users.noreply.github.com>\n\nGithub-Pull: #34093\nRebased-From: c1361fc42dd60606fcd6273cede1083cd88866a2\n",
        "signature": "-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\niQIzBAABCAAdFiEEz7FuIclQ9n+pXlWPLuufXMCVJsEFAmmhh4MACgkQLuufXMCV\nJsFIMhAAmSM3ZFH4DSsG/yqD9j+lUKVI4/v3vbAHkWJYSIFawUadXmZ4AcbEeaib\nkHc+Pderw4LlzuFqfx9kJ4p+zYdu11uGT67htbxHbgdUP2fVq4ZlC/B7/lNKjmVt\nD7hnGtR4UuJfP13ZxJR2TZuVPyNIvZ9GL7V5fjXa6EwWTxm39jyFV11Awnf/L2WV\nUdOEB3Q/WE9gWsxdNtFTOMxs3GwdQb7689eSlNy2fwFlVszxIKucTR6MSbPTwodK\nLdZUxtJFtRuqBHtFrB29RFP8K4Gn1kElpNi5oR/S13rVy1zuN9j8YJnjBukaiKSx\n35Guplf58+eW23QlOmPhj+nc5mgt/mUn/lhZNwiYLN+nc1KNBq5tis01XOeYJ87f\ncGE14UyHRKohktQ2TmHOeFYs/clqVzRoaxrSiIp1jIdOxwapSkEJNFPfIZyZw2Pn\nkJRU9Cqs5OopjIIBj9osL71SKq7Tw0XR5FCBUbe1DGjgV5mCem1V8M4aeU4IAJYZ\nFgZtbkIBoK2okwAxf0xtfxANeWiUJgVymPRUrvzVDqOfaHrJHt4XNiA+tiG/7DSA\ncPWFdM1Mj8eMrJnQ11aqx5XnQf2wM3cktgIZBs0GPqfhp/Ihyq3nY0JkJBJ0+uiV\nVe36LUe/JgPBBYFQvCVoyyUfWDKl1pEqfL0xuytfL8UGq2VCevA=\n=+jc9\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----"
